title: Vanilla Black
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, International, Organic, Western, Beer/Wine, Gourmet
description: London vegetarian restaurant, near Chancery Lane Tube Station, off Chancery Lane. Aims to elevate meat-free cookery to a level that delights discerning palates of all tastes. Has a vegan menu with 2 choices per course over a 3-course menu.
